  <Summary>This issue has three short stories. The first has Cerebus in a tavern writing "On Governing." After telling Cerebus a gruesome tale, the man next to Cerebus spills some ale on his book (see comic book cover). The second has some cutesy "Elfguest" (an Elfquest parody) elves visit him. The third has Lord Silverspoon teach Cerebus how to play "Priestess," a card game.</Summary>
